{
  "_README": "ONE config file drives the whole tracker (scraper + dashboard). Edit it by hand, or generate it from your CV using docs/cv-to-config-prompt.md. After editing, commit it and re-run the workflows. All matching is case-insensitive substring on the JOB TITLE unless noted.",

